des: José Godoy singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Christian Franklin.
José Godoy doubles (2) on a fly ball to right fielder Kevin Graham.   Dustin Harris scores.

José Godoy grounds into a double play, second baseman Sheng-Ping Chen to shortstop Jancarlos Cintron to first baseman Pavin Smith.   Dustin Harris to 3rd.    Elier Hernandez out at 2nd.    José Godoy out at 1st.
